DIFFERENT WAYS OF FAILING THE PIPELINE ISSUES 
---------------------------------------------
QUESTIONS:-
-----------------
1. HOW DO YOU HANDLE JOB FAILURES IN A ETL PIPELINE ?
==========================================================================================================
--IDENTIFY THE ISSUES:-CHECK LOGS , ERROR MESSAGES, AND NOINTORING TOOLS(AZURE MONITOR, DATABRICKS LOGS)
===========================================================================================================
--RETRY MECHANISM :-     SETUP AUTOMATIC RETRIES FOR TRANSIENT FAILURES.
===========================================================================================================
--ALERTING  :-           CONFIGURE ALERTS IN ADF OR LOGIC APPS
===========================================================================================================
--FIX THE ROOT CAUSE:-   UPDATE HE SCRIPTS ,IMPORVE THE ERROR HANDLING , OR INCREASE RESOURCES.
===========================================================================================================
